lead_paragraph: Chinese investors are close to agreeing an 80 percent stake buy in football club in AC Milan and will acquire the remaining 20 percent in the next two to three years, the China Daily newspaper reported on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Chinese Investors Close to AC Milan Stake Buy-China Daily
